    <div class="col-md-12">
        <p> So I postponed the packing to tonight or tomorrow and preferred to work on the blog instead. I started looking for a bakery to get a dry bun against hunger and then sit down in a cafe somewhere with a milkshake. </p>
        <p> I found a nice small shop in a side street and the display said, "Calories high 15. Cookies, popcorn, cream cakes." Luckily I have self-control and only ordered one pineapple fruit shake without extra sugar. Some time later, lunch hunger made itself known and the cafe filled up. Then I made my way to a restaurant with a beach view. I stayed there for some time and enjoyed the view before heading back to the apartment, as work was slowly calling again. </p>
        <p> Oh, one more thing. I'm going diving again tomorrow. Looking forward to it. </p>
